<font color="#FF0000">WAR</font><br>
<tt>Sun Feb 16  1:54:55 US/Eastern 1997
</tt><p>
War is not neat, clean or tidy. It sucks. It scares the shit out of people. It scares the shit out of their families. And it leaves families without their sons ... daughters ... brothers ... sisters ... fathers ... mothers. <br>
Do not ever be seduced by our action in Desert Storm. War, any war, reaches deep inside and grabs every one of us in the private place where we live. It grabs us in our most intimate and vulnerable selves like a shark snacking on our entrails.<br>
Do not let it happen ... without making a difference ... without making someone hear your voice ... for the sake of our children ... and their children.<br>
Do not mistake our elected representatives as leaders ... we are the leaders.<br>
We can not remain silent ... visit the Wall ... and commit to ... NEVER AGAIN.<br><br>

<p><code>-- rcolb arch  (Roy E Colbert) </code><p>


